<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2012/08/16/video-introduction-to-spring-data-neo4j">Video: Introduction to Spring Data Neo4j</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon news-and-events"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/news">News and Events</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/9f9dd00242d5ef6eea53e66b2cb6bf6d?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/cjackson">Chloe Jackson</a>
 </div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2012-08-16 00:57:00.0">August 16, 2012</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="555" href="/blog/2012/08/16/video-introduction-to-spring-data-neo4j#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p> View this webinar for a practical guide to get started with Spring Data Neo4j the integration library for the <a href="http://neo4j.org">Neo4j</a> graph database. This webinar is the perfect complement to the <a href="https://bit.ly/sdn-book">Good Relationships book</a> and is aimed toward those interested in quickly learning how to get started using <a href="http://springsource.org/spring-data/neo4j">Spring Data Neo4j</a>. </p>
<p> During this webinar we will cover: </p>
<ul>
<li>Spring Data Neo4j's features and benefits</li>
<li>Spring Data Neo4j use case: A twitter-graph app using Spring Data Neo4j with Spring Social</li>
<li>Step by step demo to get started working on Spring Data Neo4j</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
