<p><br> In related news, the Cloud Foundry Open Tour is coming to India next month! If you want to hear thought leaders and experts and learn <a href="http://opentour.cloudfoundry.com/india/2012">about cloud computing, platform-as-a-service, architecture and Spring, then be sure to register now for either the Bangalore or Pune events</a>.<br> I look forward to seeing you there!</p>
